h%20parents%20were%20the%20proverbial%20%26quot%3Bhelicopters%26quot%3B%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsnowplow-parents-calling-employers-college-helicopter-parenting-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecircle%20many%20only%20children%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20In%20our%20little%20unit%2C%20my%20mom%20(then%20a%20nurse%20practitioner)%20was%20the%20breadwinner.%20My%20dad%2C%20a%20writer%2C%20was%20able%20and%20willing%20to%20handle%20childcare.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20of%20rising%20costs%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fborn-free-birth-in-america-documentary-ricki-lake-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ematernal%20health%20risks%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20I%20probably%20won't%20have%20children.%20My%20parents%20never%20overtly%20pressured%20me%20to%20do%20anything%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20do.%20Still%2C%20as%20their%20only%20child%2C%20I%20feel%20guilty%20for%20depriving%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228ea23425-e1ca-4467-bb3c-ba95fbac27f8%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20parents%20encouraged%20me%20to%20achieve%20my%20goals%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20definition%2C%20my%20family%20structure%20(with%20a%20breadwinner%20mom%20and%20stay-at-home%20dad)%20was%20quietly%20defiant%2C%20leaving%20me%20pretty%20unfazed%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwomen-double-standards-sexism-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esocial%20gender%20norms%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20societal%20norms%20aren't%20the%20only%20source%20of%20pressure%20to%20reproduce.%20My%20parents'%20priorities%20were%20selfless%3A%20They%20prioritized%20my%20happiness%20and%20career%20and%20supported%20me%20far%20beyond%20the%20legally%20required%2018%20years.%20Neither%20demanded%20that%20I%20start%20my%20own%20family%20or%20carry%20on%20theirs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFalling%20short%20of%20my%20parents'%20deepest%20inner%20hopes%2C%20though%2C%20or%20depriving%20my%20mom%20of%20some%20fulfillment%20she'd%20never%20%3Cem%3Eask%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20me%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20a%20different%20form%20of%20guilt%20altogether.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonly-child-desire-multiple-children-family-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBeing%20an%20only%20child%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20means%20I%20bear%20%3Cem%3Esole%3C%2Fem%3E%20responsibility%20for%20our%20family's%20grandchildren.%20It's%20dizzying%20when%20my%20only%20childhood%20fostered%20high%20expectations%20about%20parenthood's%20depth%20and%20lifespan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20all%20the%20more%20melancholy%20when%20I%20see%20how%20my%20mom%20delights%20in%20her%20two%20%26quot%3Bgrand-cats.%26quot%3B%20Over%20Thanksgiving%2C%20as%20we%20devised%20food%20combinations%20and%20presentations%20they'd%20find%20palatable%2C%20I%20could%20feel%20the%20joy%20a%20grandchild%20would%20bring.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20parents%20elevated%20my%20wants%20for%20decades.%20Am%20I%20failing%20them%20by%20not%20reciprocating%20with%20my%20own%20child%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226354f0e3-e0a4-4a3a-8d9c-79df276ee747%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20mom%20has%20helped%20me%20financially%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20I've%20transitioned%20out%20of%20law%20practice%2C%20I've%20taken%20only%20reproductive%20justice%20cases%20in%20Arizona.%20I've%20seen%20the%20costs%20and%20crises%20parents%20must%20navigate%2C%20from%20health%20and%20safety%20to%20education%20and%20employment.%20When%20systems%20fail%20or%20children%20fall%20through%20the%20cracks%2C%20it's%20hard%20not%20to%20imagine%20my%20potential%20kids%20in%20that%20position.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20mom%20has%20supported%20me%20as%20I've%20started%20a%20new%20career%20in%20media.%20Both%20public%20interest%20law%20and%20media%20are%20career%20paths%20equated%20with%20austerity.%20I%20worry%20that%20I'll%20never%20be%20able%20to%20afford%20the%20same%20financial%20support%20for%20my%20own%20child.%20As%20my%20mom%20nears%20retirement%2C%20would%20we%20have%20to%20choose%20between%20elder%20care%20and%20childcare%3F%20Neither%20my%20parent%20nor%20my%20child%20would%20deserve%20that%20existential%20threat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225bcfaf4b-1ef6-422a-80b1-7d99c3115b63%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20can't%20afford%20to%20be%20the%20only%20parent%20either%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20parents'%20roles%20sheltered%20me%20from%20the%20reality%20of%20many%20heterosexual%20parents.%20My%20dad%20was%20often%20the%20only%20male%20parent%20in%20sight%20after%20school%20or%20supervising%20playdates.%20He%20was%20reliable%20and%20attentive%20to%20non-verbal%20communication.%20He%20even%20French-braided%20my%20hair.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20knew%20then%20that%20we%20were%20unusual%20(and%20frankly%2C%20I%20heard%20my%20dad%20get%20disproportionate%20praise%20for%20parenting%20his%20own%20child)%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20realize%20the%20extent%20until%20I%20began%20dating.%20My%20male%20partners%20%E2%80%94%20across%20states%2C%20schools%2C%20families%20of%20origin%2C%20and%20on-paper%20beliefs%20%E2%80%94%20brought%20baffling%20paradigms%20into%20our%20relationships.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20experiences%20represent%20a%20larger%20trend%20of%20labor%20division%20for%20heterosexual%20couples.%20Many%20women%20like%20me%20aren't%20seeking%20partnership%20with%20any%20man%20who's%20tacitly%20accepted%20this%20culture.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat's%20a%20challenge.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EWithout%20a%20p