a%20and%20Australia%20had%20its%20fair%20share%20of%20controversies%20with%20a%20number%20of%20them%20revolving%20around%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20dressing%20room.%20With%20India%20losing%20the%20series%203-1%20and%20failing%20to%20retain%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%20after%2010%20years%2C%20there%20were%20many%20reports%20of%20a%20rift%20in%20the%20team%20and%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E's%20lack%20of%20form%20did%20not%20help%20matters.%20A%20report%20in%20the%20Indian%20Express%20claimed%20that%20a%20senior%20player%2C%20who%20called%20himself%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Fix-It%26quot%3B%20pitched%20himself%20as%20an%20interim%20captain.%20Former%20India%20star%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Robin%20Uthappa%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F738-robin-uthappa-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERobin%20Uthappa%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20to%20social%20media%20to%20criticise%20the%20unnamed%20cricketer%20for%20taking%20a%20selfish%20stand.%20In%20a%20recent%20interview%2C%20he%20broke%20his%20silence%20on%20the%20rant%20and%20explained%20what%20he%20felt%20about%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20the%20kind%20of%20person%2C%20if%20something%20is%20going%20on%2C%20I%20directly%20mention%20it.%20In%20the%20team%2C%20I%20know%20people%20individually.%20But%20when%20a%20tour%20is%20going%20on%2C%20a%20tournament%20is%20going%20on%2C%20I%20don't%20talk%20to%20any%20of%20them%20because%20every%20player%20has%20his%20own%20routine%20and%20mindset.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20it%20doesn't%20feel%20right%20to%20enter%20into%20their%20space.%20So%20I%20don't%20talk%20to%20anyone%20during%20a%20tournament%2C%20nor%20do%20I%20message%20anyone%2C%20even%20if%20they%20play%20good%20or%20bad.%20If%20they%20are%20playing%20bad%2C%20then%20I%20do%20drop%20a%20message%20to%20motivate%20them.%20If%20they