es-to-victims-of-floods-in-somalia%2Famp_articleshow%2F117115974.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arvind%20Kejriwal%20vs%20BJP's%20Parvesh%20Verma%2C%20'Purvanchal'%20Remark%20Sparks%20Protest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP's%20charges%20against%20the%20BJP%20over%20alleged%20changes%20in%20the%20electoral%20rolls%20a%20month%20before%20the%20polls%20and%20against%20BJP%20leader%20Parvesh%20Verma%20have%20led%20to%20a%20fresh%20showdown%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20vying%20for%20power%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20yesterday%20ordered%20a%20probe%20by%20its%20chief%20electoral%20officer%20in%20Delhi%20after%20a%20delegation%20led%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%20filed%20a%20complaint%20against%20Mr%20Verma%2C%20who%20is%20contesting%20against%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20from%20the%20New%20Delhi%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%20on%20Friday%2C%20Mr%20Verma%20said%20he%20was%20open%20to%20any%20investigation%20and%20that%20his%20only%20aim%20is%20to%20defeat%20Mr%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20AAP%20did%20nothing%20in%2011%20years.%20They%20didn't%20listen%20to%20the%20people's%20perils.%20AAP%20did%20not%20give%20out%20jobs%20in%20the%20last%2011%20years.%20They%20are%20scared%20of%20losing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20AAP's%20allegations%20of%20violating%20the%20Model%20Code%2C%20he%20said%20he%20had%20only%20asked%20the%20companies%20he%20knew%20to%20meet%20those%20looking%20for%20jobs%20in%20his%20constituency.%20Claiming%20he%20did%20not%20ask%20for%20votes%20for%20giving%20jobs%2C%20he%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20problem%20does%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20have%20if%20some%20people%20get%20jobs%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EShowdown%20Over%20'Purvanchal'%20Remarks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal's%20remarks%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20bringing%20people%20from%20Bihar%20and%20UP%20to%20create%20%26quot%3Bfake%20votes%26quot%3B%20