%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E%20bet%20big%20on%20Copilot%2C%20its%20generative%20artificial%20intelligence%20chatbot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20released%20Copilot%20in%202023%2C%20and%20rapidly%20rolled%20it%20out%20across%20various%20products%20and%20softwares.%20The%20company%20markets%20Copilot%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20help%20users%20with%20productivity%20tasks%20such%20as%20drafting%20a%20memo%20for%20work%2C%20adding%20to%20or%20amending%20hectic%20calendars%2C%20analyzing%20a%20spreadsheet%20or%20a%20few%20lines%20of%20code%2C%20or%20even%20writing%20a%20poem%20or%20short%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20combing%20the%20vastness%20of%20the%20internet%20in%20fractions%20of%20a%20second%20to%20source%20troves%20of%20information%20and%20then%20engaging%20in%20machine%20learning%20and%20informed%20prediction%2C%20Copilot%20can%20create%20content%3B%20it%20can%20analyze%2C%20interpret%2C%20and%20explain%20extant%20data%3B%20and%20it%20can%20create%20systems%20for%20planning%20and%20managing%20many%20aspects%20of%20your%20life%2C%20from%20work%20to%20recreation%20to%20hobbies%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20Copilot%20will%20be%20the%20new%20UI%20that%20helps%20you%20gain%20access%20to%20the%20world's%20knowledge%20and%20your%20organization's%20knowledge%2C%20but%20most%20importantly%2C%20it%20will%20be%20your%20agent%20that%20helps%20you%20act%20on%20that%20knowledge%2C%26quot%3B%20Microsoft%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ceo-satya-nadella-career-rise%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESatya%20Nadella%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20during%20a%20keynote%20address%20at%20Microsoft's%20annual%20Microsoft%20Ignite%20business%20conference%20in%20November%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20long%20after%20Copilot's%20launch%2C%20industry%20experts%20predicted%20that%20for%20the%20fiscal%20year%202024%2C%20Copilot%20would%20generate%20billions%20for%20the%20company.%20However%2C%20the%20AI%20tool%20