22_blank%5C%22%3EWindows%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Macs%2C%20and%20both%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%3C%2Fa%3E%20iOS%2C%20and%20Android%20mobile%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20use%20Microsoft%20Copilot%20in%20many%20programs%20that%20you%20likely%20already%20use%2C%20including%20Microsoft%20Teams%2C%20Microsoft%20Word%2C%20Microsoft%20Excel%2C%20Microsoft%20PowerPoint%2C%20OneNote%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-how-to-write-email-outlook-ai-could-help-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOutlook%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20more.%20It%20can%20assist%20you%20in%20rapidly%20creating%20and%20editing%20documents%2C%20spreadsheets%2C%20presentations%2C%20and%20more%2C%20acting%20both%20as%20your%20content%20creator%20and%20an%20editor%20and%20sort%20of%20AI%20coworker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20basic%20version%20of%20Microsoft%20Copilot%20is%20free%20to%20use%20on%20the%20web%2C%20in%20Windows%2C%20with%20a%20Mac%20OS%2C%20and%20with%20Android%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-ios%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiOS%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20free%20version%20includes%20access%20to%20GPT-4%2C%20GPT-4%20Turbo%2C%20and%20GPT-4o%20during%20non-peak%20times.%20It%20also%20allows%20users%20to%20create%20and%20edit%20AI%20images%2C%20use%20plugins%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20is%20also%20a%20paid%20version%20of%20Copilot%20called%20Copilot%20Pro%2C%20which%20offers%20more%20advanced%20features%20and%20better%20access.%20Copilot%20Pro%20includes%20all%20the%20features%20of%20the%20free%20version%2C%20plus%20priority%20model%20access%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20use%20Copilot%20in%20Microsoft%20apps%20like%20Word%2C%20Excel%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-powerpoint%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPowerPoint%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Outlook%2C%20and%20OneNote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20use%20Copilot%20Pro%2C%20you%20need%20a%20Microsoft%20365%20Personal%20or%20Family%20subscription%2C%20which%20costs%20%246.99%20per%20month%20for%20a%20personal%20subscription%20and%20%249.99%20per%20month%20for%20a%20family%20subscription%2C%20good%20for%20up%20to%20six%20users.%20With%20Copilot%20Pro%20added%2C%20the%20total%20cost%20is%20around%20%2426.99%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2273dff13e-d3ad-4853-9904-fa8ac07380a9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20Microsoft%20Copilot%20better%20than%20ChatGPT%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20smartphone%20displays%20icons%20for%20AI%20apps%20including%20Gemini%2C%20ChatGPT%2C%20and%20Copilot.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675b738ccf8d1359a2dfb2a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMicrosoft's%20Copilot%20AI%20tool%20has%20a%20number%20of%20competitors%2C%20including%20Google's%20Gemini%20and%20ChatGPT.%3Cp%3EJaque%20Silva%2FNurPhoto%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20ways%20and%20for%20some%20uses%2C%20Copilot%20can%20be%20more%20effective%20than%20ChatGPT.%20Copilot%20is%20better%20for%20quick%2C%20tactical%20tasks%20that%20come%20about%20during%20your%20workflow%2C%20while%20ChatGPT%20is%20more%20commonly%20used%20for%20broader%20tasks%20and%20conversational%20AI%2C%20like%20for%20writing%20a%20creative%20story%20or%20rehearsing%20before%20a%20meeting%20or%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECopilot%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Microsoft%20ecosystem%20and%20can%20easily%20pull%20information%20from%20across%20Microsoft%20applications%2C%20which%20can%20be%20helpful%2C%20and%20it%20can%20also%20reply%20to%20questions%20with%20visual%20responses%2C%20such%20as%20photos%20and%20images.%20Also%2C%20unlike%20ChatGPT%2C%20which%20doesn't%20provide%20sources%20for%20its%20responses%2C%20Copilot%20does%2C%20making%20cross-referencing%20and%2