%3A%22This%20Woman%20Is%20Connecting%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Floriculture%20Farmers%20to%20City%20Markets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmidst%20the%20lush%2C%20rolling%20hills%20of%20Mao%2C%20a%20little%20girl%20would%20hurry%20home%20from%20school%2C%20her%20footsteps%20quickening%20as%20the%20scent%20of%20fresh%20earth%20and%20wildflowers%20filled%20the%20air.%20Her%20parents%2C%20hardworking%20farmers%2C%20would%20be%20in%20the%20fields%3B%20she%20would%20eagerly%20lend%20a%20hand%2C%20carrying%20baskets%20of%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20from%20the%20farm%2C%20her%20small%20hands%20carrying%20whatever%20little%20weight%20they%20could.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20in%20the%20quiet%20corners%20of%20the%20land%2C%20where%20a%20patch%20of%20flowers%20bloomed%2C%20that%20she%20found%20the%20most%20comfort.%20There%2C%20tending%20to%20her%20lot%20with%20the%20same%20care%20her%20parents%20had%20taught%20her%2C%20she%20would%20look%20at%20their%20delicate%20beauty%2C%20unaware%20that%20these%20moments%20spent%20nurturing%20those%20flowers%20would%20turn%20into%20a%20vision%20that%20would%20connect%20the%20hills%20of%20Mao%20to%20the%20cities%20far%20beyond.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMao%2C%20in%20Manipur%2C%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359452%2Fflower-gardening-business-portulaca-farming-by-kerala-alappuzha-engineer-making-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20%E2%80%9Cland%20of%20flowers%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20known%20for%20its%20lush%2C%20organic%20produce%20and%20its%20people%E2%80%99s%20love%20for%20nature.%20Chokhone%20Krichena%2C%20the%2032-year-old%20founder%20of%20Dianthe%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%2C%20is%20leveraging%20these%20sentiments%20to%20help%20floriculture%20farmers%20by%20bridging%20the%20gap%20between%20rural%20growers%20and%20urban%20consumers.%20By%20helping%20backend%20farmers%20get%20market%20access%2C%20she%20is%20giving%20th