25%20higher%20prices%20than%20the%20market%20rate%20as%20an%20incentive%20for%20their%20quality%20produce.%20The%20company%20provided%20primary%20processing%20services%2C%20including%20grading%2C%20sorting%2C%20and%20cleaning%20of%20the%20millets%2C%20before%20selling%20them%20to%20bulk%20clients%20down%20south.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202020%20and%202021%2C%20Heart%20in%20Hills%20helped%20me%20earn%20approximately%20Rs%204%20lakh.%20I%20could%20repay%20my%20loans%20and%20purchase%20essentials%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Subdei%20(78)%2C%20from%20Luthiyag%20village%2C%20Rudraprayag%20district.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%2C%20traders%20would%20buy%20from%20me%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20pay%20me%20fairly.%20Now%2C%20I%20am%20capable%20enough%20to%20run%20my%20business%2C%20trading%20pulses%20and%20millets.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3780_11zon-1735049817-500x667.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Foreka%20aims%20to%20train%20women%20farmers%20so%20they%20can%20help%20in%20increasing%20the%20sales%20of%20the%20cold-pressed%20oils%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3780_11zon-1735049817-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3780_11zon-1735049817-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3780_11zon-1735049817-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3780_11zon-1735049817-1152x1536.jpg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3780_11zon-1735049817-1536x2048.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3780_11zon-1735049817-900x1200.jpg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3780_11zon-1735049817-600x800.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3780_11zon-1735049817-450x600.jpg%20450w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3780_11zon-1735049817-300x400.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3780_11zon-1735049817-150x200.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3780_11zon-1735049817-1200x1600.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3780_11zon-1735049817-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3780_11zon-1735049817.jpg%201805w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-392182%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EForeka%20aims%20to%20train%20women%20farmers%20so%20they%20can%20help%20increase%20the%20sales%20of%20cold-pressed%20oils%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20running%20a%20large-scale%20venture%20was%20not%20easy.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20traders%20felt%20threatened%20by%20our%20model.%20They%20were%20used%20to%20controlling%20the%20market%2C%20but%20we%20believed%20in%20the%20power%20of%20direct%20trade%2C%E2%80%9D%20Satyam%20says.%20Despite%20their%20venture%20causing%20some%20tension%20in%20the%20local%20markets%2C%20he%20and%20his%20team%20pressed%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20soon%20the%20young%20entrepreneur%20realised%20that%20offering%20higher%20incentives%20to%20farmers%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20enough%20to%20sustain%20long-term%20growth.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20business%20became%20increasingly%20seasonal%2C%20with%20supply%20chain%20challenges%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20maintain%20consistent%20operations.%20So%2C%20we%20had%20to%20stop%20our%20operations%20in%20Uttarakhand%20and%20come%20up%20with%20a%20better%20approach%20to%20expand%20our%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20cold-pressed%20oil%20brand%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20second%20COVID-19%20wave%2C%20he%20and%20his%20team%20noticed%20an%20increasing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328846%2Fsibi-manivannan-runs-gramiya-cold-pressed-oils-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edemand%20for%20cold-pressed%20oils%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20insight%20led%20them%20to%20pivot%20their%20business%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202022%2C%20the%20Heart%20in%20Hills%20team%20ventured%20into%20the%20cold-pressed%20oil%20market%20with%20the%20launch%20of%20Foreka%20in%20Rajasthan.%20This%20expansion%20was%20made%20possible%20by%20the%20support%20Satyam%20received%20in%20November%202020%2C%20when%20he%20was%20awarded%20a%20prestigious%20fellowship%20from%20The%20Buddha%20Institute%2C%20founded%20by%20Ved%20Arya%2C%20an%20alumnus%20of%20IIM%20Ahmedabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Buddha%20Institute%20provided%20us%20with%20a%20generous%20grant%20of%20Rs%2022%20lakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%2C%20which%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20enabling%20the%20team%20to%20scale%20their%20operations.%20Their%20research%20into%20the%20region%20highlighted%20a%20high%20rate%20of%20outmigration%2C%20presenting%20an%20opportunity%20to%20create%20local%20employment.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20exceptional%20quality%20of%20mustard%20seeds%20in%20the%20area%20made%20it%20an%20ideal%20location%20for%20their%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20partnered%20with%20NGOs%20like%20SRIJAN%20to%20establish%20a%20value%20chain%20for%20farming%2C%20offering%20farmers%20better%20prices%20and%20resources%20to%20test%20seed%20quality.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20supporting%20farmers%20directly%2C%20we%20ensured%20fair%20prices%20and%20sustainable%20practices%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Satyam.%3C