ved%20my%20identity%20as%20just%20a%20transwoman%20who%20is%20HIV%20positive%2C%20Dr%20Joseph%20saw%20my%20potential%20and%20motivated%20me%20to%20start%20the%20trust%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20I%20named%20the%20trust%20SIP%20in%20memory%20of%20my%20three%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20Selvi%2C%20Indira%2C%20and%20Pazhani%20%E2%80%94%20who%20tragically%20lost%20their%20lives%20to%20HIV%2C%E2%80%9D%20Noori%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20Trust%20aimed%20to%20create%20awareness%20and%20outreach%20for%20HIV%20positive%20individuals.%20Later%2C%20Noori%20started%20focusing%20on%20rescuing%20infants%20and%20children%20who%20were%20abandoned%20because%20of%20HIV.%20%E2%80%9CHaving%20experienced%20a%20challenging%20childhood%20myself%2C%20I%20deeply%20understand%20the%20lasting%20impact%20that%20parents%20and%20caregivers%20have%20on%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20mindset.%20These%20children%20are%20not%20to%20blame%20for%20their%20HIV%20status%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Noori%20has%20dedicated%20her%20life%20for%20these%20children%2C%20saving%20nothing%20for%20herself.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645-300x226.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645-500x376.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645-768x577.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebett