or%20cultivation.%20Sarbeswar%2C%20too%2C%20became%20involved%20in%20clearing%20and%20preparing%20the%20land%20for%20farming.%20He%20leased%20a%2012-acre%20plot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20formal%20training%20but%20a%20strong%20willingness%20to%20learn%2C%20Sarbeswar%20began%20farming%20with%20traditional%20methods.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20what%20I%20saw%20other%20elders%20doing%20%E2%80%94%20growing%20eggplant%2C%20chilli%2C%20Assam%20lemon%2C%20and%20other%20vegetables%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarbeswar%20recalls.%20However%2C%20the%20methods%20proved%20insufficient%2C%20and%20the%20land%20lacked%20the%20fertility%20needed%20to%20sustain%20a%20profitable%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitial%20hurdles%20like%20inadequate%20finances%20for%20investment%20into%20agriculture%2C%20lack%20of%20proper%20facilities%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20knowledge%20of%20scientific%20methods%20were%20always%20present.%20Chirang%20was%20a%20backward%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20admits%2C%20reflecting%20on%20his%20early%20challenges.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20learnt%20a%20great%20deal%20about%20agriculture%20while%20working%20on%20that%20leased%20land.%20After%20years%20of%20working%20on%20other%20people%E2%80%99s%20land%2C%20I%20bought%20a%20small%20piece%20of%20land%20in%201995.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEager%20to%20learn%20more%2C%20an%20impromptu%20visit%20to%20the%20agriculture%20department%2C%20in%201998%2C%20became%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20Sarbeswar.%20From%20there%2C%20he%20began%20working%20closely%20with%20the%20department%2C%20learning%20about%20agriculture%2C%20improving%20yields%2C%20finding%20ways%20to%20increase%20his%20profits%20each%20season%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20intercropping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EVenturing%20into%20integrated%20farming%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPopular%20in%20Assam%2C%20the%20areca%20nut%20crop%20takes%20years%20to%20start%20yielding.%20Even%20when%20they%20do%2C%20the%20yields%20are%20often%20not%20as%20high.%20%E2%80%9CInstead%20of%20depending%20solely%20on%20one%20crop%2C%20I%20had%20learnt%20about%20intercropping%20and%20how%20it%20could%20be%20helpful%2C%20even%20necessary%2C%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sarbeswar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20number%20of%20people%20in%20a%20family%20increases%2C%20the%20land%20keeps%20getting%20smaller.%20To%20survive%2C%20we%20need%20to%20grow%20multiple%20crops%20each%20year%2C%20and%20have%20harvests%20in%20every%20season%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20He%20initially%20grew%20arecanuts%2C%20but%20over%20time%2C%20added%20three%20to%20four%20more%20crops%20like%20bananas%20and%20turmeric%2C%20to%20ensure%20a%20steady%20income%20throughout%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20profits%20improved%20a%20lot.%20I%20kept%20trying%20new%20farming%20methods%20and%20realised%20that%20intercropping%20was%20the%20key%20to%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-20-at-8.42.28-AM_11zon-1734710623.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sarbeswar%20stands%20in%20a%20room%20adorned%20with%20hanging%20plants%2C%20showcasing%20the%20practice%20of%20sericultur%5Cn%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebett