20farming%20became%20the%20best%20option%20for%20me.%20Having%20someone%20like%20Sarbeshwar%20to%20guide%20me%20has%20been%20crucial%20in%20my%20family%E2%80%99s%20financial%20stability%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20For%20the%20upcoming%20season%2C%20Purno%20has%20planted%20cacao%20on%20four%20acres%2C%20intercropped%20with%20areca%20palm%20trees%2C%20and%20has%20also%20introduced%20king%20chilli%20alongside%20watermelon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBringing%20fish%20farming%20into%20the%20mix%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarbeswar%E2%80%99s%20dedication%20to%20improving%20his%20farming%20practices%20led%20him%20to%20seek%20out%20training%20and%20knowledge%20from%20various%20sources.%20In%202007%2C%20he%20attended%20a%20week-long%20training%20provided%20by%20the%20fishery%20department%2C%20which%20opened%20his%20eyes%20to%20the%20potential%20of%20integrating%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F294631%2Fassam-woman-uses-innovatove-ras-technology-for-land-based-fish-farming-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efish%20farming%20with%20agriculture%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20soil%20we%20had%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20very%20fertile%2C%20so%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20yield%20good%20crops.%20We%20thought%20that%20if%20we%20created%20a%20pond%20with%20fish%20in%20it%2C%20it%20might%20yield%20better%20results%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarbeswar%20decided%20to%20incorporate%20aquaculture%20into%20his%20farming%20practices%2C%20using%20a%20combined%202.5%20acres%20of%20his%20land%20for%20five%20different%20ponds.%20These%20ponds%20are%20home%20to%20fingerlings%2C%20and%20he%20practices%20pisciculture%20for%20about%2010%20months%20each%20year.%20Initially%2C%20Sarbeswar%20attempted%20to%20harvest%20the%20fish%20at%20the%20standard%20six-month%20mark%20but%20found%20the%20profits%20to%20be%20unsatisfactory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20c